menu "HM-10 BLE Bridge Configuration"

    config HM10_DEVICE_NAME
        string "Target HM-10 Device Name"
        default "HMSoft"
        help
            The name of the HM-10 device to connect to.
            Common names: HMSoft, sallen_hm10

            You can find the device name using a BLE scanner app.

    config HM10_DEVICE_MAC
        string "Target HM-10 Device MAC Address (optional)"
        default ""
        help
            Optional: Connect by MAC address instead of name.
            Format: AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF

            Leave empty to search by name only.
            If specified, this takes priority over device name.

endmenu
